          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/774914-sheila?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/774914-sheila?shelf=feminism">feminism</a>
